title: Benghazi hearing, Paul Ryan and post-Biden political landscape
text:
First topic: A preview of Hillary Clinton's testimony before the House Select Committee on Benghazi 
Guest: David Graham. He covers politics and global news for the Atlantic. Second topic: Will Paul Ryan be the next Speaker? 
Guest: Lisa Mascaro, congressional correspondent for the Los Angeles Times and other Tribune newspapers Third topic: Early primaries, Joe Biden 
Guest: Jason Johnson, political science professor at Hiram College
